{"tid":2230360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今年雙十全民感謝日搞手疑似有問題!!!","createTime":"2020-10-05T01:04:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T06:50:24.000Z","uid":318702,"like":21,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3fd9870566766c4e311191eb2887ed83fd96f5c2","tid":2230360,"uid":318702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:04:43.000Z","msg":"相信食黃店幫襯黃店已是大家嘅日常<br />\n<br />\n今年有個雙十全民感謝日<br />\n<br />\n有別於舊年嘅模式<br />\n<br />\n去年只係隨便幫襯一間, 有支持即可<br />\n<br />\n今年則需報名參加並且支付$300至$500嘅&rdquo;文宣設計費&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n今次搞手嘅目的真係如佢地所講嘅咁<br />\n<br />\n定係想從中掠一筆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有朋友識得其中嘅搞手<br />\n<br />\n怒斥佢係不理政治不吃人間煙火嘅貪錢港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁嘅人點解突然間會咁落力幫助黃圈？<br />\n<br />\n雖然&rdquo;文宣設計費&rdquo;話就話可以唔俾<br />\n<br />\n但有幾多黃店會唔俾？<br />\n<br />\n咁收到嘅&rdquo;文宣設計費&rdquo;會唔會透明公開？<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">希望今次搞手可以公開明細<br />\n<br />\n由收到邊間黃店嘅&rdquo;文宣設計費&rdquo;及其金額<br />\n<br />\n以至點用、最後剩低嘅錢去向都可以公布出黎</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望大家一腔熱情支持黃店黃色經濟圈嘅同時都小心被有心人利用賺錢<br />\n<br />\n畢竟已不是第一次有人利用「黃」嚟搵錢呃人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26598a559434f8df272e366077188c050b813f7","tid":2230360,"uid":318702,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:04:58.000Z","msg":"自推10"},{"pid":"bf13d0694e13f1194eaff5bcd21877480380a27c","tid":2230360,"uid":318702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:05:08.000Z","msg":"自推9"},{"pid":"b88febd3480a0f3062b5e0f04393de6cd84041fb","tid":2230360,"uid":318702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:05:19.000Z","msg":"自推8"},{"pid":"88efcc72f10366dd8ff70987d9c44de61a755c1e","tid":2230360,"uid":318702,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:05:29.000Z","msg":"自推7"